name: CHAINLINK GIRL
description:
#12 of #50 in the Crypto Girl Collection.
Chainlink Girl provides reliable and real-world data to smart contracts on the blockchain.  Get within her reach and she will link you up and lock you down.  

The first owner of this NFT will receive a 24x36 museum quality print hand signed by Ellie Gonsalves aka Crypto Girl (digital copy also available instead of physical print if desired).
